            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Dianae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublius</ex></expan> Antonius <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ubli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uirina</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Antoninus aedilis <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>desig</abbr><ex>natus</ex></expan> signum mar<lb break="no" n="5"/>moreum <expan><abbr>cultorib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Dianae et Mercuri <lb n="7"/>sua pecunia dedit <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>idemq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> dedicavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>2 Fragmente; Maße beziehen sich auf Fragment a; Höhe Fragment b: (42,5) cm.</p>
